      <data key="d1">ENGINEERING_CONTROL</data>
      <data key="d2">A standards-based engineering control specifying ventilation requirements for healthcare settings to manage indoor air quality and support infection control. The citation indicates the ASHRAE/ASHE Standard 170-2008 as the reference framework for design and operation of ventilation in clinical environments.</data>
