      <data key="d1">EFFECTIVENESS_MEASURE</data>
      <data key="d2">A tracer-based exposure metric: the fraction of emitted CO2 that is inhaled at different cabin locations. Used to infer relative exposure to rebreathed air in mannequin-based tests.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.68</data>
      <data key="d4">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee_chunk_4</data>
