      <data key="d0">STATIONARY TESTS WITH MANNEQUINS</data>
      <data key="d1">VALIDATION_STUDY</data>
      <data key="d2">Stationary mannequin experiments measuring inhalation volume of CO2 relative to emitted CO2 (P_CO2) to characterize spatial exposure patterns. Missing data points were imputed using the average of surrounding data.</data>
