      <data key="d2">An engineering control that reduces airborne exposure by bringing in outdoor air, exhausting indoor air, and using filtration/directional airflow within HVAC systems. In the provided record, it appears as a MeSH term indicating its relevance to controlling indoor airborne particles.</data>
